schema_summary: Military Overlay is a geodatabase containing a collection of military feature templates for Planning, Operations, and Intelligence use. It contains an information model for creating Military Features based on MIL-STD-2525D.

schema_summary: Military Features is a template for creating a geodatabase of military features for Planning, Operations, and Intelligence use. It contains an information model for creating Military Features based on MIL-STD-2525D.

schema_use: Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
